OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780935073
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for historical
OL,4,Csex abuse of pupil
OL,6,FA former Salford teacher has been
OL,7,Fjailed for 15 years after being
OL,8,Fconvicted of a series of child sex
OL,9,Foffences against a schoolgirl.
OL,11,FGary Day-Davies, 55, of Tyldesley, was
OL,12,Fsentenced at Liverpool Crown Court on
OL,13,FMonday 8 June after a jury found him
OL,14,Fguilty of three counts of rape, three
OL,15,Fcounts of sexual assault and one count
OL,16,Fof sexual assault by touching a child.
OL,18,FThe offences took place between 2006
OL,19,Fand 2009 while Day-Davies was teaching
OL,20,Fat a school in Salford.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
