OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780935073
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for historical
OL,4,Csex abuse of pupil
OL,6,FThe court heard he abused his position
OL,7,Fof trust by inviting the girl to his
OL,8,Fhome for extra tuition, where he gave
OL,9,Fher alcohol and drugs before sexually
OL,10,Fabusing her.
OL,12,FFurther abuse took place on school
OL,13,Fpremises, including in the library and
OL,14,Fa classroom store cupboard, the court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FThe survivor reported the abuse to
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Police in 2022,
OL,19,Ftriggering a lengthy investigation
OL,20,Fwhich led to Day-Davies being charged
OL,21,Fand brought to trial.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780935073
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for historical
OL,4,Csex abuse of pupil
OL,6,FDuring proceedings, Day-Davies denied
OL,7,Fthe allegations and claimed the victim
OL,8,F"must have just held a bit of a
OL,9,Fgrudge" against him.
OL,11,FIn a statement read to the court, the
OL,12,Fsurvivor described the verdict as a
OL,13,Fturning point in her life.
OL,15,FShe said: "Since receiving the news of
OL,16,Fthe guilty verdicts, I feel like an
OL,17,Fenormous weight was lifted off my
OL,18,Fshoulders. The emotional trauma bond
OL,19,Fthat I have endured for the last 20
OL,20,Fyears has finally severed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780935073
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for historical
OL,4,Csex abuse of pupil
OL,6,FShe added that while the conviction
OL,7,Fhad brought her a sense of justice and
OL,8,Fclosure, she still faced a long
OL,9,Fjourney of recovery.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Dave Ogden, of
OL,12,FGMP's Criminal Investigation
OL,13,FDepartment in Salford, praised the
OL,14,Fsurvivor's courage in coming forward.
OL,16,FHe said: "Time is no barrier when it
OL,17,Fcomes to being sexually abused. No
OL,18,Fmatter how long ago it was, we will
OL,19,Flisten to you, investigate and act
OL,20,Frobustly against perpetrators."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
